.name
WBLink
.author
Dave Schreiber
.description
WBLink put an "AppIcon" on the Workbench screen that makes a hard link to
any file or directory that is dropped on it.  Enhancements to the previous
version include bug fixes and the ability to allow the user to specify where
the AppIcon should be placed on the screen.
.type
Workbench Tool
.version
1.10
.source
Full C source included.
.distribution
Copyright but Freely Redistributable
.requirements
Workbench/Kickstart 2.0 or later.
.short
AppIcon to make hard links, V1.10, C src
